# Listing

This script retrieves a list of elements from various sources.
The elements can be pages, posts or both. They can also be filtered by categories or tags.

The script uses the page attribute:

- `page.listing.source`: An optional hash containing the source of the listing

If the any of `paginator` or `page.paginator` are defined, then the list of elements
will be limited to the appropriate elements for the current page.

The resulting list of elements is returned in a variable `listing__elements`.

## Input parameters

- `page.listing.source`: {{ page.listing.source | debug }}
- `page.listing.paginator`: {{ page.listing.paginator | debug }}
- `paginator`: {{ paginator | debug }}

